{"title":"sessionStorage","uid":"7aee2a9e36929c61e8acfa41e36e3c28","slug":"sessionStorage","date":"2023-07-07T17:03:01.991Z","updated":"2023-07-07T17:03:43.590Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/sessionStorage.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>#HTML</p>\n<h1 id=\"概念\"><a href=\"#概念\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"概念\"></a>概念</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p> sessionStorage 是 HTML5 新增的一个会话存储对象，用于临时保存同一窗口 (或标签页) 的数据（key&#x2F;value），在关闭窗口或标签页之后将会删除这些数据。是 window 下的对象。</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"特点\"><a href=\"#特点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"特点\"></a>特点</h1><ul>\n<li>网页存储 api，允许存储 key–value 形式的数据<ul>\n<li>value 值为字符串类型</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>当用户结束会话时，sessionstorage 的数据也会清除<ul>\n<li>重新加载仍然会保持</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>同源 same origin 数据可以访问，用于存储暂时数据，例如购物车，表单数据</li>\n<li>打开相同 url 的 tab 页面，创建各自的 sessionStorage</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"Api\"><a href=\"#Api\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Api\"></a>Api</h1><h2 id=\"存储数据\"><a href=\"#存储数据\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"存储数据\"></a>存储数据</h2><p><code>sessionStorage.setItem(&#39;key&#39;, &#39;value&#39;);</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"删除数据\"><a href=\"#删除数据\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除数据\"></a>删除数据</h2><p><code>sessionStorage.removeItem(&#39;key&#39;);</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"读取数据\"><a href=\"#读取数据\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"读取数据\"></a>读取数据</h2><p><code>sessionStorage.getItem(&#39;key&#39;);</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"清除所有\"><a href=\"#清除所有\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"清除所有\"></a>清除所有</h2><p><code>sessionStorage.clear();</code></p>\n","text":"#HTML 概念 sessionStorage 是 HTML5 新增的一个会话存储对象，用于临时保存同一窗口 (或标签页) 的数据（key&#x2F;value），在关闭窗口或标签页之后将会删除这些数据。是 window 下的对象。 特点 网页存储 api，允许存储 key–va...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":481,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"HTML","slug":"HTML","count":14,"path":"api/tags/HTML.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">概念</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">特点</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Api\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Api</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"